HEADWORD: Uncult
<hw>Un*cult"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets>
not + L. <ets>cultus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>colere</ets> to cultivate. Cf.
<er>Incult</er>.]</ety> <def>Not cultivated; rude; illiterate.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

